sources.description:
Amnesiac gunman Jericho is rescued and befriended by a charismatic, itinerant cowboy-preacher named Joshua. Together they survive certain danger, while the gunman searches to find the answer to his lost identity. After seven years of wandering, Jericho unravels the mystery of his past and finds his destiny in the town of Jericho.

2000.  Stars: Mark Valley, Leon Coffee, R. Lee Ermey
